comments: Hart (NYK) momentarily rests a hand on Murray (ATL) before retracting it, and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Robinson (NYK) avoids making contact with the ball during Murray's (ATL) driving shot attempt.
Murray (ATL) slides his hand off Hart's (NYK) right arm before separating near the baseline.
Hunter (ATL) and Hart (NYK) briefly engage following the pick, and the contact is marginal.
Hart (NYK) initiates contact with Johnson's (ATL) right arm and affects his SQBR as he attempts to control the ball. The contact occurs prior to Johnson's upward shooting motion.

Replay review of the foul called on Quickley (NYK) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Quickley reaches in and makes contact with Young's (ATL) right arm as he begins his upward shooting motion, affecting the jump shot attempt. Young is correctly awarded three free throws.
Capela (ATL) and Robinson (NYK) both engage as they pursue the loose ball.
Johnson (NYK) takes a small step laterally, causing marginal body contact to occur with Brunson (NYK) at the start of his drive, which he is able to move through.
Randle (NYK) brings an arm across Young's (ATL) front and initiates contact that affects his SQBR during the driving shot attempt.
Robinson (NYK) is trailing Murray (ATL) when marginal body contact occurs as he is jumping toward the basket to contest Murray's driving shot attempt.
Murray (ATL) makes clean contact with the ball and cleanly dislodges it away from Randle (NYK) prior to any incidental contact occurring.
Boganovic (ATL) commits a take foul on Quickley (NYK).
Capela (ATL) is firming up on his left foot as he establishes a screening position and does not deliver illegal contact to Hart (NYK) as it occurs to his side.
Bogdanovic (ATL) is the last person to touch the ball as his shot goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to NYK.
DiVincenzo (NYK) does not release the ball within 5 seconds.
Brunson (NYK) commits a take foul on Murray (ATL).
Murray (ATL) steps over the plane of the free throw line before the ball touches the basket ring, backboard or the free throw ends.
